import React from 'react'
import {Outlet} from 'react-router-dom'

import Header from './Header'
import Footer from './Footer'

const Layout = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Header/>
                <Outlet/>
            <Footer/>
        </>
    )
}
export default Layout
